        {
            "title": "印度盧比跌至紀錄低點 市場擔心美國關稅影響",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 印度盧比兌美元匯率跌至紀錄低點，市場擔憂美國50%關稅將衝擊印度經濟成長和企業盈利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盧比下跌0.4%，至1美元兌87.9763盧比，跌破今年2月創下的87.9563前期歷史低點。受外資持續撤離本地股市影響，盧比成為今年亞洲表現最差的貨幣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著本周美國新關稅生效，印度貨幣承壓。這些關稅針對紡織品、鞋類和珠寶等出口密集型產業。花旗預計，關稅可能使印度年度經濟增速被削弱0.6-0.8個百分點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Indian Rupee Falls to Record on Worries Over US Tariff Impact</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%9B%A7%E6%AF%94%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E6%93%94%E5%BF%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-081525969.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 16:55:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
